import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class Timeline extends Component { render() { return (
highlights

Timeline

Member Technical Staff at ManageEngine, Zoho Corp Division 2018-Present

I have joined the ManageEngine's NetFlow Analyzer as a Software Developer. My major part of the work has been into the field of developing and maintaining Network monitoring software .

Internship at ManageEngine, Zoho Corp Division 2017-2018

I joined the ManageEngine (Zoho Corp Division) as a Software Developer-Intern in the ManageEngine's NetFlow Analyzer team. Worked with peers to understand the product and develop features based on the customer requirements and developed Network traffic analysis based on ip address groups.

Undergraduation at SKCT2014-2018

I am pursued my under-graduation studies with major in IT.(Information Technology). I have taken courses like DSA, OOPs, Computer Networks, Advanced Java Programming, Web-Data Management over the years and have better understanding of these subjects.I have also awarded for my Academic Excellence in third year.

Higher Education 2012-2014

I have completed my higher secondary education with major subjects as Physics,Chemistry & Maths. During my time at school, I have developed interest in solving complex problems of the fundamental physics which helped me to improve my understanding of any problem and also my mathematical skills to actually solve the problems.

) } }
